{"tid":1479964,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"明天出街, 請自行組隊互保照應","createTime":"2019-08-17T06:06:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T09:23:12.000Z","uid":198175,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9b6bc9ed6608a5adadd60b3875d0197918b33729","tid":1479964,"uid":198175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T06:06:51.000Z","msg":"明天出街, 請自行組隊互保照應, 以防俾鬼滲透<br />\n<br />\n一係一家人出去, 一係一班朋友出去, 帶齊嘢隨時保護自己同身邊嘅人.<br />\n<br />\n出到去人多地方等待時, 最好同左右唔識的人主動打招呼, 傾吓計交流吓, 大家講多幾句就知係咪啱啱大陸落嚟, 係同路人就最好一齊活動, 不要分散落單, 時刻保持聯絡, 留意四周, 互相照應.<br />\n<br />\n如遇到D問極都唔出聲, 不明廣東話/英文, 戴耳機, 持有長棍物體, 不時影大頭, 玩W7的可疑人物混集其中, 尤其以年輕大隻男性居多, 請隨時注意該批人士動向, 並保持適當距離.<br />\n<br />\n如何組隊反滲透<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1458861/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1458861/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n如何用共知的目標同行動守則嚟反滲透<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1469214/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1469214/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"fe01e02035be0b29f653d255d8783b8691b7d356","tid":1479964,"uid":198175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T06:07:07.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"a86a61ad0ee24ece08bbcce8093a107774d26ed8","tid":1479964,"uid":198175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T06:08:01.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"58e721b95860dde0abc9f515d8bd395109569d10","tid":1479964,"uid":36089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T06:09:16.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，借一借位~<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>保護自己資產，全民唱美元現鈔！</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1478882\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1478882</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e2a9fc1e6f82820cc7e2900e4f985836cbfbbf64","tid":1479964,"uid":36089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T06:09:29.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，借一借位~<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>保護自己資產，全民唱美元現鈔！</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1478882\" data-aut